387
00:19:29,910 --> 00:19:31,653
Estamos sempre a dormir

388
00:19:31,654 --> 00:19:35,407
E estamos a dormir
com as pessoas erradas

389
00:19:35,808 --> 00:19:39,239
"Going Down Swinging",
do Fall Out Boy.

390
00:19:39,853 --> 00:19:42,057
Tens senso de humor,
rapaz.

391
00:19:43,890 --> 00:19:45,210
Obrigado, Ralph.

392
00:19:45,211 --> 00:19:47,811
Um complexo de Deus carregado,
